    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag! It\u2019s been super well-maintained and is ready for its next adventure. You're going to love how it handles on the road. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering high-revving performance through six individual throttle bodies. This example is paired with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. Crucially for the chassis' longevity, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS unit has been overhauled with upgraded seals. The rod bearings have also been addressed, ensuring the bottom end is secured for high-RPM operation. The suspension remains taut with Bilstein dampers, providing the precise turn-in these cars are known for. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals are robust and the power delivery is linear and aggressive. A true driver's car that has been maintained with technical precision.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Maintenance up to date. Minimal interior wear. Runs and drives smoothly.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
