      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the robust 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant, delivering linear power through its 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a well-maintained multi-link rear suspension geometry that ensures precise turn-in and cornering stability. The naturally aspirated induction provides immediate throttle response, while the four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers offer consistent, fade-resistant deceleration. Recent service includes a verification of the IMS bearing and RMS, ensuring the mechanical integrity of the valvetrain and bottom end. A driver-focused machine with an excellent power-to-weight ratio and communicative hydraulic steering.",
